#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.96"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.96:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.96:0.2"
msgid "9. Gaṅgāpeyyālavagga"
msgstr "9. Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.96:0.3"
msgid "96. Chaṭṭhapācīnaninnasutta"
msgstr "96. Sixth Discourse on Slanting East"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.96:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yā kācimā mahānadiyo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, all the great rivers—that is,"

msgctxt "sn45.96:1.2"
msgid ""
"gaṅgā, yamunā, aciravatī, sarabhū, mahī, sabbā tā pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā "
"pācīnapabbhārā;"
msgstr ""
"the Ganges, Yamunā, Aciravatī, Sarabhū, and Mahī—slant, slope, and incline "
"towards the east."

msgctxt "sn45.96:1.3"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold "
"path slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn45.96:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path slant, slope, "
"and incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn45.96:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … "
"sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.96:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path "
"slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.96:1.7"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
